accessibility.text: Actually you have no idea why you know the words like \"sunrise\" and \"green\", they just suddenly jump into your head, like a part of your past life.
Sitting up and looking around, you notice that there is a flock of some giant animals moving slowly away from you, maybe that causes the vibration just now.
Thinking for a while, you decide to ignore them and think about your situation or walk closely and see what they are doing.
